import React from 'react'

import { Grid, Segment, Card } from 'semantic-ui-react'
import '../stylesheets/userConsole.css'


const Fight = (props) => { 
	return (
		<Card.Group>
			<Card fluid color='red'>
				<Grid id='fightgrid' columns='equal'>
					<Grid.Row stretched>
					<Grid.Column>
						<Segment>1</Segment>
						<Segment>2</Segment>
					</Grid.Column>
					
					<Grid.Column>
						<Segment>1</Segment>
						<Segment>2</Segment>
					</Grid.Column>
					</Grid.Row>
				</Grid>
			</Card>
		</Card.Group>
	)
}

export default Fight;
